title: No app updates in Google Play Store
content:
I have pixel 3a running Android 11 Jan 2021 security patch . Recently from past 5 days iam not getting any updates from the Google Play Store. And it shows no updates available whenever I go to the update section. I don't know this is happening only to me or everyone. Currently iam running Google Play Store version  23.1.30-21. Is this the latest version or new version available. I tried to clear cache storage. Still it's showing no updates available. 
Please help me
